              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12764648124800321355">The world-famous story of Santa Claus coming to a house and bringing presents in lyrical form - and here also nicely illustrated by Jan Brett.<br/><br/><img src='https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1608828579i/30582765._SX540_.jpg' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/><br/><br/><img src='https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1608828579i/30582766._SX540_.jpg' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/><br/><br/>Wonderfully atmospheric and joyful - a classic for very good reason and one I always love to read again!</span>
  <span id="freeText12764648124800321355" style="display:none">The world-famous story of Santa Claus coming to a house and bringing presents in lyrical form - and here also nicely illustrated by Jan Brett.<br><br><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1608828579i/30582765._SX540_.jpg" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><br><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1608828579i/30582766._SX540_.jpg" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><br>Wonderfully atmospheric and joyful - a classic for very good reason and one I always love to read again!</span>
